('vpn_configuration_guide', 'How to Install and Configure the Corporate VPN', 'To install and configure the Corporate VPN:
1. Open your browser and navigate to https://vpn.company.com.
2. Log in with your corporate credentials and download the VPN client installer for your OS.
3. Run the installer and follow the on-screen instructions.
4. Once installed, open the VPN client and enter ''vpn.company.com'' as the server address.
