('outlook_configuration_guide', 'How to Set Up Your Outlook Profile', 'To set up a new Outlook profile for your corporate email:
1. Open the Control Panel on your PC and search for ''Mail (Microsoft Outlook)''.
2. Click ''Show Profiles...'' and then click ''Add''.
3. Enter a name for the new profile and click OK.
4. Enter your Name, Corporate Email Address, and Password, then click Next.
5. Outlook will automatically configure your server settings. Click Finish.
