('vpn_connection_howto', 'How to Connect to the VPN', 'To connect to the corporate VPN once it is already installed:
1. Locate the VPN client icon in your system tray (bottom right on Windows, top right on Mac).
2. Click the icon and select ''Connect''.
3. Enter your corporate username and password when prompted.
4. Approve the Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) request sent to your mobile device.
